stimulus: In this experiment, you will see some aliens talk and make judgments about what they are talking about.

This is Dax the alien. He speaks an alien language.

He says, "Difu Dax midaku."
That means "Hello, my name is Dax."

Dax has a box.
He opens the box and looks inside.

Then, Dax says, "Toma zem zorp bidaku midu osh gipu!"

Which box do you think Dax was looking in when he said
"Toma zem zorp bidaku midu osh gipu!"?

responses: {"Q0":"Something about the phrase suggested the idea of mixed up shapes."}

stimulus: This is the end of the study. Thank you for participating!
